data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!! Quick move out time. Enjoy the views in all seasons from this majestic home in desirable Morgan Pointe. Single level living offering open living space, granite countertops, HWF, crown molding, laundry room & primary suite on main floor. So much more to offer with a completed lower level providing add'l living space. Lower level open living space with laminate flooring, recessed lighting, trey ceiling, crown molding, office area, gathering room, kitchenette, & 1 1/2 baths. Gorgeous back yard. New roof 2023 and new heat pump 2021. Garage size 21.1 W x 21.8 D. See it today! Ask about a VA assumable loan with low interest rate! Taxes, measurements, lot size subject to verification.
